  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Armored Shark",
      "effect": "(This card is always treated as an \"Armored Xyz\" card.)\nYou can send 1 WATER Xyz Monster from your Extra Deck to the GY, then target 1 Fish monster in your GY with a Level equal to the sent monster's Rank; Special Summon it. During your opponent's turn, if this card is in your GY (Quick Effect): You can target 1 WATER Xyz Monster you control; equip this card to it as an Equip Spell that gives it 500 ATK. You can only use each effect of \"Armored Shark\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
